        <item>
            <title>Spotify HiFi 高音質串流或 2025 年推出，多項增值功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 01:55:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[spotify hifi]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1292571</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Spotify 自 2021 年首次宣佈計劃推出 HiFi 無損音質串流服務後，用家已經苦等多年。根據最新消息，這項名為「Music Pro」的新高階訂閲計劃，或將於 2025 年內正式推出。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">「Music Pro」計劃除了提供無損音質串流外，還將加入一系列額外功能，例如歌曲混音、演唱會門票折扣、優先購買權，以及搶先聽音樂或參與音樂會問答會等特權。據估計，這項服務的額外收費約為每月 5 至 6 美元（約港幣 39 至 47 元），相比 Spotify 現時 Premium 計劃（11.99 美元/月）價格更高。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Spotify 近期為此與 Warner Music Group 和 Universal Music Group 簽訂多年的授權協議，解決版權問題，同時探索更多超級粉絲專屬的服務，如獨家欣賞派對和高質版專輯內容等。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">值得留意的是，目前 Apple Music 和 Amazon Music 已在基本訂閲計劃中提供無損音質服務，Spotify 則希望透過「Music Pro」的附加功能為用家帶來更高價值，並在競爭激烈的音樂串流市場中突圍而出。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">多年來，Spotify 用家對 HiFi 串流的期待從未減退，而在 2025 年，這項高音質體驗終於有望成為現實。</span></p><p><b>來源：</b><a href="https://www.theverge.com/news/614091/spotify-music-pro-hifi-streaming-service-release-date-2025"><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Verge</span></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025/fun-tech/">Spotify HiFi 高音質串流或 2025 年推出，多項增值功能</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>暫列史上最賣座電影第 8 位  《哪吒 2》超越《頭腦特工隊 2》成全球動畫票房冠軍</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/nazha-no1-animation/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nazha-no1-animation</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/nazha-no1-animation/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 01:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mario]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[哪吒]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[哪吒 2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[頭腦特工隊]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1292554</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《哪吒之魔童鬧海》自 2025 年 1 月 29 日於中國內地上映以來，全球票房已突破 16.98 億美元（約港幣 132.44 億元），超越《頭腦特工隊 2》，躍居全球動畫電影票房榜首。燈塔專業版數據顯示，該片票房仍持續增長，最終票房預測超過 150 億人民幣（約港幣 162 億元），成為全球動畫電影史上新霸主。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218221850-694x395.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="395" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218221850-694x395.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218221850.jpg 924w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>由導演餃子執導的《哪吒之魔童鬧海》（下稱:哪吒 2）延續前作世界觀，講述哪吒與敖丙歷經天劫後靈魂雖存，但即將魂飛魄散，太乙真人嘗試以七色寶蓮重塑二人肉身，卻在過程中遭遇重重挑戰。與 2019 年上映的《哪吒之魔童降世》相比，本片在製作層面大幅升級。數據顯示，前作鏡頭數為 1,864 個，其中特效鏡頭 1,400 個，而《哪吒 2》鏡頭數量增至 2,427 個，特效鏡頭更達 1,948 個，超越前作全片總鏡頭數，視覺效果明顯提升。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292555" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/s_e8baec60662249c495-264x580.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/s_e8baec60662249c495-264x580.jpg 264w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/s_e8baec60662249c495.jpg 409w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 264px" /></p><p>《哪吒 2》不僅在中國市場表現出眾，於全球市場亦取得突破。不少在海外影迷讚揚其技術水準已達國際級，與美國、日本動畫巨頭作品相提並論。但另一方面，也有人質疑票房數據是否經過包裝，甚至認為影片票房主要依靠中國市場內部支持，才推升至如此高峯。社交媒體上，支持與反對聲音引發激烈討論，然而票房表現已成事實，無可否認。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292556" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218215709-532x580.jpg" alt="" width="532" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218215709-532x580.jpg 532w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218215709.jpg 599w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 532px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">資料截至 2025 年 2 月 18 日</p><p>《哪吒 2》的全球票房佳績也引起國際媒體關注。部分外媒對該片成功感到驚訝，認為動畫電影市場競爭激烈，能夠突破迪士尼、皮克斯等美國動畫巨頭作品實屬難得。然而，業界普遍認為，下一部有望挑戰票房冠軍的動畫電影將是 2026 年 4 月上映的《超級瑪利歐兄弟電影版 2》。</p><p>來源: <a href="https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202502180281.aspx">cna</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/nazha-no1-animation/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Dreame V18S Aqua 5 合 1  吸塵洗地器優惠碼 + unwire 讀者入 CODE 換贈品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/18/dreame-v18s-aqua/shop_guide/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dreame-v18s-aqua</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/18/dreame-v18s-aqua/shop_guide/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 13:34:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[買物情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dreame]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dreame V18S Aqua]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1292490</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>想輕鬆吸塵、拖地，重可以除蟎、顯塵？你可以試用早前我們介紹過的全新 Dreame V18S Aqua 五合一全方位旗艦級吸塵器，一次過滿足你 5 個願望。Unwire.hk 讀者只要輸入我們的折扣碼「DreameUnwire」 ，就可以領取限量禮品包贈品： 1L 清潔液 + 洗地滾刷（總值 HKD 368）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1292544 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dreamehkv18saqua01mj-398x580.jpg" alt="" width="398" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dreamehkv18saqua01mj-398x580.jpg 398w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dreamehkv18saqua01mj.jpg 408w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 398px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1292545 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025021821h30-694x538.jpg" alt="" width="744" height="577" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025021821h30-694x538.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025021821h30.jpg 1025w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 744px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_68550"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cnGj3ItVrwg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2>Step 1 前往官方網站</h2><p>首先前往 Dreame 官方網站，將 V18s Aqua 加入購物車。</p><p>網站連結：<a href="https://www.dreametech.com.hk/products/v18s-aqua">https://www.dreametech.com.hk/products/v18s-aqua</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b1-687x580.jpg" alt="" width="687" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b1-687x580.jpg 687w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b1.jpg 1065w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 687px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲將 V18s Aqua 加入購物車</p><h2>Step 2 搜尋 V18S 清潔套裝 (贈品)</h2><p>點擊這個連結：<a href="https://www.dreametech.com.hk/products/%E8%BF%BD%E8%A6%93-dreame-h14-pro-%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%A5%97%E8%A3%9D-%E8%B4%88%E5%93%81-%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6">連結</a></p><p>或者點擊放大鏡開啟搜尋欄，輸入「V18S 清潔套裝 (贈品)」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊放大鏡</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b5-694x457.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="457" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b5-694x457.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲輸入「V18S 清潔套裝 (贈品)」後再點擊箭嘴指住的放大鏡</p><p>瀏覽器會跳頁至下面畫面，點擊綠框購物袋即可加入至購物車。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b9-664x580.jpg" alt="" width="664" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b9-664x580.jpg 664w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b9.jpg 1031w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 664px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊購物袋將「V18S 清潔套裝 (贈品)」加入至購物車</p><h2>Step 3 開啟購物車、輸入優惠碼並結賬</h2><p>現在請開啟你的購物車，確認吸塵器以及「V18S Aqua 清潔套裝」都已經加入購物車，點擊結帳。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b11-694x492.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="492" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b11-694x492.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b11.jpg 822w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「結帳」</p><p>看見下圖結帳畫面，請點擊「訂單摘要」，然後在「禮品卡」欄目輸入優惠碼「DreameUnwire」，點擊套用即可獲得贈品：1L 清潔液和洗地滾刷（總值 HKD368），之後按照指示填寫個人資料付款即可。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b12-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b12-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b12.jpg 825w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「訂單摘要」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1292541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892416-694x554.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892416-694x554.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892416.jpg 1127w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在禮品卡位置輸入優惠碼「DreameUnwire」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1292542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892426-638x580.jpg" alt="" width="638" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892426-638x580.jpg 638w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892426.jpg 990w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 638px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲經套用後，有關贈品便會變成免費</p><p>購買網址: <a href="https://hktvmallredirect.com/W27gpFAt">https://hktvmallredirect.com/W27gpFAt</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
