            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>DJI Osmo Mobile 手機穩定器已來到第 7 代了，今代又有什麼改進呢？不過小編更感興趣的是剛收到的 DJI Phantom 4 積木呢！</p><p><a title="_DSC7210" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335400886/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335400886_7621542aa4_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7210" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p>早前 DJI 官網發出的產品預告宣傳圖，正是 DJI Osmo Mobile 新增的多功能追蹤模塊，即外置 Tracker，亦是第 7 代的賣點，其實其他的功能都與上代差不多，穩定器的外觀設計也是差不多；而另外有分別的就是第７代會分為兩個版本，Osmo Mobile 7P 及 Osmo Mobile 7，主要分別如下：</p><p>Osmo Mobile 7P：黑色為主色，附有多功能追蹤模塊，內建延長桿可伸展延長。<br />
Osmo Mobile 7：灰色為主色，沒有多功能追蹤模塊，需另購；穩定器不可伸展延長。</p><p><a title="_DSC7171" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335400696/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335400696_72cb783e22_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7171" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Osmo Mobile 7P 與 Osmo Mobile 7 的包裝盒</p><p><a title="_DSC7204" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631443/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631443_918ca61438_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7204" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Osmo Mobile 7P 明顯較長</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC7205" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631418/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631418_f693bdf929_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7205" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC7206" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335400881/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335400881_f9a983402f_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7206" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Osmo Mobile 7P 附有多功能追蹤模塊</p><p><a title="_DSC7177" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631238/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631238_8702cc4424_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7177" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Osmo Mobile 7P</p><p><a title="_DSC7193" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631123/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631123_c8739fb434_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7193" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">7P 內建延長桿</p><h2>多功能追蹤模塊 Tracker 主要功能</h2><p>基本上現世代的手機拍片都已非常穩定，再加上用了穩定器後，畫面穩定情況大家都已經知道，而 DJI 雲台增穩效果一向也不錯，這方面也不用特別多説，反而是這個多功能追蹤模塊又有何乾坤？現在講講它的主要功能。</p><p><a title="_DSC7180" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335620759/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335620759_94d3e2b261_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7180" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">正面設有補光燈及鏡頭</p><p><a title="_DSC7181" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495677/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54334495677_7804c54b37_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7181" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7182" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335818915/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335818915_54df178f5f_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7182" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">補光燈，以及開關鍵</p><p><a title="_DSC7183" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495657/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54334495657_c71fa65fe4_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7183" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7184" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631168/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631168_b857f7e74c_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7184" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7203" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335620989/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335620989_56f67e79b4_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7203" width="1600" height="1067" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><strong>1. 智能跟拍</strong><br />
手機連上追蹤模塊後，可以立即採用手機的相機 App 便可使用 Tracker 追蹤，或者用 Mimo App 也可。亦可搭配直播軟件、視頻會議軟件及語音通話時使用智能跟隨。多功能追蹤模組可前後切換，支援前後鏡頭的跟拍。</p><div style="padding: 46.15% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="ScreenRecording_02-18-2025 14-24-38_1" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1057840024?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p>&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;</p><div></div><div></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1d080f119b074d388399-694x556.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="556" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1d080f119b074d388399-694x556.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1d080f119b074d388399.jpg 1124w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><p style="text-align: center;">Tracker 的各項設定</p><p><strong>2. 色溫與亮度補光</strong><br />
提供四檔色溫與四檔亮度調節，這方面對於自拍的用家最為用得著；而 OM7P 可透過側面波輪控制補光燈，滑動波輪調節亮度或色溫。</p><p><a title="_DSC7198" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631038/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631038_9fe9f3db75_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7198" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7202" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495917/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54334495917_95bcc8b18d_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7202" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">滑動波輪調節亮度</p><p><strong>3. 收音功能</strong><br />
可與 DJI Mic Mini 發射器連上收音，提升影片的收音質素。</p><p><a title="_DSC6179" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335819040/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335819040_0bf452be02_h.jpg" alt="_DSC6179" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7173" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495672/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54334495672_2ce7572446_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7173" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Tracker 亦可單獨購買</p><h2>OM7 定價抵玩</h2><p>而穩定器方面，OM7P 與 OM7 升級了雲台結構，展開雲台只需一步，按下關機鍵後，雲台會自動回到可折疊的位置，一步即可折疊，適合新手快速使用。另外今代續航力亦非常強，可以使用 10 小時，絕對足夠一天的拍攝。另外值得留意的是，OM7P 售價為 HK$979，而 OM7 則是 HK$599，今代 OM7 的定價又幾抵玩啊～</p><p><a title="_DSC7192" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631128/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631128_5566d19ca4_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7192" width="1067" height="1600" /></a></p><p>售價：<br />
DJI OM7P：HK$979<br />
DJI OM7：HK$599<br />
DJI OM7 Tracker：HK$329</p><h2>同場加映：Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 積木</h2><p>小編收到 DJI 送出的賀年套裝，內有其中一樣最為值得與讀者分享的，就是這套 Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 積木，還記得當年小編第一次買的航拍機，就是 Phantom 2，當時是沒有圖傳也沒有雲台，要另購安裝上機身，而鏡頭則是用上了 GoPro 3，當年出外航拍時是要放入小型的行李喼中，所以小編對於 Phantom 的機種，特別有感覺的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d295cc0225224e278d2a-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d295cc0225224e278d2a-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d295cc0225224e278d2a-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/e448c88c65634155a02d-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/e448c88c65634155a02d-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/e448c88c65634155a02d-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292532" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ceccc5b8cce94a15b53e-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ceccc5b8cce94a15b53e-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ceccc5b8cce94a15b53e-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>本以為這套 Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 積木，很快便可以砌好，原來設計都很講究，積木採用 1:1.6 的比例，總數有 817 塊，除了還原了 Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 的外型外，另一半是採用了透明殼的設計，讓你透視到內部的機件架構，所以透視那邊的就有更多的積木要砌了；另外航拍機的另一個象徵就是其四個螺旋槳，內建有齒輪結構，你只要轉動其中一隻槳，就會連動另外三隻螺旋槳一起轉動。小編完成它需時大約 5 小時，另外要注意的是內部的機件架構有些位置較為複雜，小型零件也較多，小心砌錯位。</p><p><a title="_DSC7155" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495737/in/d